text:
Geting this error while running the build process. Build process continues 
after the error.

A nonfatal internal JIT (3.10.107(x)) error 'Relocation error: NULL relocation t
arget' has occurred in :
  'org/apache/crimson/parser/Parser2.maybeComment (Z)Z': Interpreting method.
creator: dmitryhaham@alliantfs.com

text:
You can ignore this non-fatal JIT problem. It is not an Ant issue and is a known
problem in the JDK, triggered by the crimson parser.
creator: conor@apache.org
